  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >World Drawn is a game in which you play as two characters who save a young girl.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Both heroes have their own unique features. The first Chuck jumps high and can throw the second hero.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Bill is short and cannot jump high, but he compensates for this by shooting from a slingshot and the ability to go where Chuck gets stuck.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Pass dangerous traps and enemies and save the lady!</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Dynamic gameplay</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Lots of enemies</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Interesting gameplay</p></li></ul>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >World Drawn is a game in which you play as two characters who save a young girl.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Both heroes have their own unique features. The first Chuck jumps high and can throw the second hero.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Bill is short and cannot jump high, but he compensates for this by shooting from a slingshot and the ability to go where Chuck gets stuck.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Pass dangerous traps and enemies and save the lady!</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Dynamic gameplay</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Lots of enemies</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Interesting gameplay</p></li></ul>",
